title: Note- If such sites are situated in zone other than SDZ and Natural Area, the FSI permissible shall
clause_text: Note- If such sites are situated in zone other than SDZ and Natural Area, the FSI permissible shall be that corresponding to the FSI permissible in the respective zones as stipulated in Table 12 of Regulation No.30(1)(A). Guidelines for identification of TDA and for development to be permitted therein
